<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your StaySync trial is ending soon</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
  <table width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #ef4444 100%); padding: 32px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px;">{{daysLeft}} days left in your trial</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px;">{{hotelName}}</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px;">
              <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px;">Hi {{customerName}},</p>
              <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                Thanks for trying StaySync. Your trial for <b>{{hotelName}}</b> ends on
                <b style="color: #ef4444;">{{trialEndDate}}</b> ({{daysLeft}} days from now).
              </p>
              <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                After that, your workspace will be <b>suspended</b>.
                We'll keep your data for 30 days before it is permanently deleted.
              </p>
              <table width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{upgradeUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
                      Upgrade now
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <p style="color: #777; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
                Need help choosing a plan? Just reply to this email and the StaySync team will help you out.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 16px; text-align: center; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">
              StaySync — Hotel Management System<br>
              Sent to {{recipient}}
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
